22:39.958 --> 22:42.860
       [unsettling music]       

23:12.891 --> 23:14.692
            [squish!]           

23:24.469 --> 23:26.002
     [Jeff sighs] Oh, Terry!    

23:26.038 --> 23:28.239
    13 words? That's all you    
