23:56.502 --> 23:59.369
  Because of what you say here. 
          "I am weak."          

23:59.404 --> 24:00.704
        Right? He's weak!       

24:00.739 --> 24:02.540
        You know, I just        
        don't want to...        

24:02.575 --> 24:04.508
        hurt Mum any more       
