25:08.740 --> 25:10.307
       He couldn't wait to      
       get away from us to      

25:10.342 --> 25:11.808
     hang out in that bloody    
        workroom of his,        

25:11.843 --> 25:13.944
   twiddling knobs and playing  
      with valves and shit!     

25:13.979 --> 25:15.746
       He spent more time       
         walking the dog        

25:15.781 --> 25:17.681
        and smoking weed        
       than being with us.      

25:17.750 --> 25:19.950
     No, no, no. Mum raised     
