   I know. No, I'm joking. No.  

26:26.752 --> 26:29.353
       Yeah. I'll... I'll       
        call you tonight.       

26:29.388 --> 26:30.220
      Alright, my darlin'.      

26:31.256 --> 26:33.223
       No, I'm being good.      
