26:33.258 --> 26:34.692
   Alright. We'll speak soon.   

26:34.727 --> 26:36.493
         See you, love.         

26:36.528 --> 26:37.995
         Why did you say        
       we've taken photos       

26:38.030 --> 26:39.663
        and you're gonna        
         send her some?         

26:39.698 --> 26:41.765
      We can't send photos.     
   We haven't got any photos!   

26:41.767 --> 26:43.667
     It's fine. Don't worry.    
      She'll never see 'em.     

26:43.703 --> 26:45.769
         No, no, no. No,        
  she's used to disappointment. 

26:45.838 --> 26:47.171
     Don't worry about that.    

26:47.206 --> 26:49.239
     Never finished a single    
  fuckin' diet she's put me on. 

26:49.274 --> 26:51.441
     No, I'll tell her that     
     you deleted 'em. Easy.     

26:51.510 --> 26:52.442
           Why have <i> I</i>           
