26:52.511 --> 26:53.677
           Alright,<i> I</i>           
          deleted them!         

26:53.712 --> 26:55.779
   Does it matter? It's fine.   
       Anyway, you're up.       

26:55.847 --> 26:58.548
      So, important thing -     
   when you're talking to Sue,  

26:58.584 --> 27:00.284
   I want you to say "Sydney"   
      as often as you can.      

27:00.353 --> 27:02.586
       Really burn it into      
   her subconscious, alright?   

27:02.621 --> 27:04.621
 - So, "Sydney, Sydney, Sydney."
         - [city noises]        

27:04.623 --> 27:07.724
  Oh, hi. It's, um... it's me.  

27:07.760 --> 27:12.362
     I'm, um... just calling    
    from, um... from Sydney.    

27:12.398 --> 27:14.464
     - [horn honks on tape]     
             - Um...            

27:14.533 --> 27:16.566
       Yeah, so, me and...      
    me and J are here and...    

27:16.602 --> 27:18.802
      it's all... it's all      
         good in Sydney.        

27:18.871 --> 27:21.404
  So, um... anyway, I'll, um... 

27:21.439 --> 27:24.741
I'll be here for... for a little
   bit... little bit longer.    

27:24.776 --> 27:26.977
 [clears throat] But I'll, um...

27:26.979 --> 27:29.313
   [clears throat] I'll, uh...  

27:29.315 --> 27:32.082
    Just thought I'd ring and   
     say hi. So, I'll, uh...    

27:32.117 --> 27:36.086
        Anyway, um... say       
         hi to the kids.        

27:36.121 --> 27:37.654
          [phone beeps]         

27:37.656 --> 27:39.657
   [clears throat, stops tape]  

27:43.729 --> 27:44.995
         That was quick.        

27:44.997 --> 27:46.763
   Yeah, couldn't get through.  

27:46.799 --> 27:49.767
     Went to her voice-mail,    
  so I... just left a message.  

27:52.738 --> 27:54.338
        [presses buttons]       

27:55.141 --> 27:56.740
       What are you doing?      

27:57.276 --> 27:58.509
              Tez.              

27:58.577 --> 28:00.344
    I'm not a fuckin' idiot.    

28:01.180 --> 28:02.780
    Why didn't you call Sue?    

28:03.849 --> 28:05.182
       You know what? Just      
        forget about it.        

28:06.651 --> 28:08.852
    Tez, I'm not gonna forget   
       about it. Alright?       

28:08.854 --> 28:12.188
    Sydney's our alibi if the   
  suicide story doesn't stick.  

28:12.257 --> 28:15.458
  Look, you're having a lovers' 
 tiff with Sue. I can see that. 

28:15.861 --> 28:18.528
 Right? But I want you to think 
     about 40 years in jail     

28:18.530 --> 28:20.464
    and get the fuck over it    
       and ring her back!       

28:20.499 --> 28:21.765
        She left me, OK?        

28:23.001 --> 28:27.004
  So now I have no alibi that's 
   not... you, Mum or Rodger.   

28:28.273 --> 28:29.373
           Happy now?           

28:30.041 --> 28:31.341
            Tch! Why?           

28:32.444 --> 28:33.977
     Why didn't you tell me?    

28:34.012 --> 28:35.211
   What does it matter to you?  

28:36.047 --> 28:37.881
   Well, I could have helped.   
        I've been there.        

28:38.483 --> 28:39.850
      I know it's not easy.     

28:39.885 --> 28:42.119
         Well, you sure         
       make it look easy.       

28:42.654 --> 28:43.887
              I do?             

28:43.889 --> 28:45.021
              Yes.              

28:45.056 --> 28:46.356
              Oh...             

28:46.391 --> 28:47.725
              Look.             

28:48.059 --> 28:48.859
             [sighs]            

28:49.862 --> 28:53.663
 We can't have any secrets with 
   each other. Not now. Right?  

28:54.399 --> 28:56.900
 If they investigate the suicide
          as a murder,          

28:57.502 --> 28:59.369
     they're gonna interview    
   more than just you and me.   

28:59.972 --> 29:02.739
  They're gonna interview Mum,  
     our families, everyone.    

29:02.741 --> 29:04.074
         And it's gonna         
       look bad if you're       

29:04.142 --> 29:05.742
         going through a        
       divorce and I'm...       

29:05.811 --> 29:07.344
             - What?            
             - What?            

29:08.847 --> 29:11.681
 Nothin'. You gotta get it right
      between you and Sue.      

29:12.317 --> 29:13.917
        Just for a couple       
