   I'm a shithouse liar, Jeff.  
         You know that.         

29:26.765 --> 29:28.198
   It's why she's leaving me.   

29:28.700 --> 29:30.000
        What do you mean?       

29:30.035 --> 29:32.168
      [sighs] She asked me      
      if I still love her.      

29:32.203 --> 29:34.103
    - What did you tell her?    
          - The truth.          

29:34.105 --> 29:36.939
 - Well, why would you do that?!
 - Because I'm a shithouse liar!

29:36.941 --> 29:38.708
