29:39.444 --> 29:42.279
     I don't love her, Jeff.    
  I'm not sure that I ever did. 

29:43.014 --> 29:44.781
       Not... not really.       

29:44.850 --> 29:46.116
    You know that's bullshit.   

29:46.118 --> 29:48.951
        No, I'm serious!        
 I've been miserable for years. 

29:48.953 --> 29:50.587
Oh, I know that. That's obvious.

29:51.123 --> 29:52.722
  No, you should have left her  
    years ago. She's a bully.   

29:52.757 --> 29:54.791
         No, I mean it's        
     bullshit you can't lie.    

29:54.793 --> 29:57.227
       Anyone can lie. You      
      just didn't want to.      

29:57.262 --> 30:00.297
   Look... tell me a lie now.   
     Make it an obvious one.    

30:00.299 --> 30:01.965
      No! I don't want to!      

30:02.034 --> 30:05.135
     I'm not asking you, I'm    
     telling you! Lie to me.    

30:06.104 --> 30:08.305
OK, so, tell you an obvious lie?

30:08.373 --> 30:09.639
              Yeah.             

30:09.641 --> 30:11.274
      Alright. How about...     

30:11.309 --> 30:14.077
 I'm <i> not</i> having second thoughts 
  about what we're doing here?  

30:14.980 --> 30:17.647
       Or I'm <i> not</i> worried       
   something's gonna go wrong?  

30:18.483 --> 30:21.451
       Or I'm <i> not</i> worried       
   as to whether I can do it?   

30:21.487 --> 30:24.821
 How about... how about I'm <i> not</i> 
 worried we're gonna get caught?

30:24.823 --> 30:26.957
 Or that I'm... not seconds away

30:26.992 --> 30:29.993
   from getting on a bike and   
  getting the fuck out of here? 

30:31.497 --> 30:32.830
          How did I do?         

