       Jesus, Tez. Look...      

30:37.836 --> 30:39.603
    Watch me. I'll show you.    

30:41.840 --> 30:43.240
              What?             

30:45.110 --> 30:46.610
             Rodger?            

30:48.580 --> 30:49.613
              He...             

