    No, you can't be serious.   

30:54.486 --> 30:56.119
         Rodger's dead?         

30:57.155 --> 30:57.921
             But...             

30:58.657 --> 31:00.324
     But that's impossible.     

31:01.426 --> 31:03.860
     No, you mu... you must     
