     OK, why would he do it?    

31:06.164 --> 31:08.966
 I mean, his wife's in hospital 
        dying of cancer.        

31:09.601 --> 31:11.301
    I mean, he's a Christian.   

31:11.970 --> 31:14.137
    He thinks suicide's evil.   

31:15.507 --> 31:17.040
            Cowardly.           

