             Listen.            

48:28.139 --> 48:30.539
      [vehicle approaches]      

48:40.585 --> 48:42.017
               Oh!              

48:42.053 --> 48:44.253
    Fuck, he's early! [pants]   

48:44.255 --> 48:47.756
 J, I don't want to do this. OK?

48:47.825 --> 48:49.391
           OK. Right.           

48:49.427 --> 48:52.027
     Remember, don't let him    
       see you until he's       

48:52.062 --> 48:54.363
       come in and closed       
      the door behind him.      

48:54.398 --> 48:56.432
         J! Did you hear        
       what I just said?!       

48:56.434 --> 48:58.767
     - Balaclava! Put it on!    
       - [car door closes]      

48:58.835 --> 49:00.436
              Move!             

49:00.905 --> 49:02.505
              Shit!             

49:15.286 --> 49:18.287
          [keys jangle]         

49:25.095 --> 49:26.929
       [whispers] What the      
        fuck's he doing?!       

49:26.964 --> 49:27.963
           [whispers]           
            Shut up!            

49:28.031 --> 49:29.465
      [keys rattle in lock]     

49:34.138 --> 49:35.538
     Do you think he knows?     

49:40.544 --> 49:43.479
   [Jeff] Oh, yeah, you've got  
     bigger problems, Rodge.    

49:46.617 --> 49:47.983
           Fuck! Fuck!          

49:48.052 --> 49:49.251
   What the fuck's he doing?!   

49:49.286 --> 49:51.153
 Round the back. Round the back!

49:59.096 --> 50:02.464
       [car pulls around]       

50:02.500 --> 50:03.632
            Oh, shit!           

50:06.671 --> 50:09.505
    - Do you think he saw us?   
     - No, I don't think so.    

50:09.507 --> 50:11.974
  He's not even inside and this 
    shit's going pear-shaped!   

50:12.009 --> 50:13.675
       - [car door closes]      
       - Rubbish! Stop it!      

50:13.677 --> 50:15.611
This is nothing! Just stay calm!

50:18.950 --> 50:21.117
      Fuck! Freddie's out!      

50:24.088 --> 50:25.520
       [Terry] What if he       
         calls the cops?        

50:25.589 --> 50:27.689
It doesn't matter if he comes in
         and finds us.          

50:27.691 --> 50:30.159
 It's our home. We haven't done 
       anything wrong yet.      

50:33.430 --> 50:34.530
              Fuck!             

50:35.632 --> 50:38.934
 OK, look. If he comes in here, 
        he didn't see us.       

50:38.969 --> 50:40.602
         Everything goes        
        as normal, right?       

50:40.637 --> 50:43.105
    If he goes to his car, he   
 spends too much time out there,

50:43.140 --> 50:44.940
  he's called the cops, right?  

50:44.976 --> 50:46.208
        We take all this        
        shit off, we tell       

50:46.277 --> 50:47.676
         him we're here         
         to see Freddie.        

50:47.711 --> 50:49.478
         OK, good. Good.        

50:50.614 --> 50:52.547
    Nup. I reckon he saw us.    
         Let's just say         

50:52.549 --> 50:54.516
     hello and forget about     
        the whole thing.        

50:54.551 --> 50:55.818
              Shh!              

50:55.853 --> 50:57.820
       [footsteps outside]      

51:16.807 --> 51:18.340
             Hello?             

51:23.314 --> 51:24.580
             Terry?             

51:25.683 --> 51:27.149
        Are you in there?       

51:29.720 --> 51:30.753
             Hello?             

51:31.489 --> 51:32.888
        [whispers] Terry.       

51:32.923 --> 51:35.023
  Answer him. Get him in here.  

51:35.058 --> 51:37.159
     Then back to our plan.     

51:38.829 --> 51:40.429
               No!              

51:43.100 --> 51:44.900
  [Rodger] If th... if there's  
       somebody in there,       

51:44.935 --> 51:48.270
  then y-you'd better get out,  
 because I-I'm calling the cops.

51:48.939 --> 51:50.238
             Terry!             

51:50.274 --> 51:53.208
    You fuckin' do it! Or you   
   and I are fuckin' finished!  

51:53.244 --> 51:55.176
Choosing Rodger over me and Dad?

51:55.212 --> 51:58.414
            - What?!            
 - You heard me! Get out there! 

52:02.553 --> 52:04.120
          [Terry] Fuck!         

52:04.956 --> 52:06.522
   - Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey!   
            - What?!            

52:08.125 --> 52:09.692
            Oh, fuck!           

52:18.969 --> 52:20.369
           Hi, Rodge.           

52:20.404 --> 52:21.704
              Hell!             

52:21.739 --> 52:22.904
          It's just me.         

52:22.939 --> 52:24.473
             Hello.             

52:29.980 --> 52:32.614
  Oh, shit, boy, you scared me! 

52:32.649 --> 52:34.483
        Sorry about that.       

52:34.485 --> 52:37.152
And you can't leave the feed out
 like that. It attracts vermin. 

52:37.721 --> 52:39.155
        And you left the        
        gate open again.        

52:40.123 --> 52:42.491
    Yeah, I was just about to   
       go back out there.       

52:43.594 --> 52:44.960
  Put the kettle on, will you?  
             I need             

52:44.995 --> 52:46.428
          something to          
        settle my nerves.       

52:47.098 --> 52:49.765
   Ticker's working overtime.   

52:53.337 --> 52:55.738
      What's going on here?     

53:00.811 --> 53:01.477
        What do you mean?       

53:02.446 --> 53:04.512
       Well, you... you're      
       not a bloody troll.      

53:04.514 --> 53:07.349
      Turn some lights on,      
         for God's sake!        

53:12.089 --> 53:14.456
     Well, the kettle isn't     
       gonna boil itself.       

53:15.125 --> 53:16.525
              Yeah.             

53:19.930 --> 53:21.497
        [picks up kettle]       

53:26.771 --> 53:29.204
      You know, I might be      
       getting old, but I       

53:29.273 --> 53:31.307
       didn't notice your       
      car in the driveway.      

53:36.681 --> 53:38.280
         Yeah, I, uh...         

53:39.683 --> 53:41.650
         ...broke down.         
      [switches kettle on]      

53:42.519 --> 53:45.553
   Oh, shit, no. How far away?  

53:45.555 --> 53:49.291
     Only about a 15-minute     
          walk or so...         

53:49.827 --> 53:51.327
            I'd say.            

53:56.968 --> 53:58.367
        Is it the Volvo?        

54:01.038 --> 54:02.238
              Mmm.              

54:02.706 --> 54:03.906
             Where?             

54:04.909 --> 54:07.576
       Uh, it was... down       
         on Dukes Road.         

54:09.146 --> 54:11.547
          Are you sure?         
   I just drove through there.  

54:12.416 --> 54:15.718
       Yeah, I... arranged      
        to have it towed.       

54:19.423 --> 54:21.390
   And what's your excuse for   
  those bloody awful overalls?  

54:22.759 --> 54:24.994
 Has there been a nuclear spill 
     I haven't heard about?     

54:25.029 --> 54:26.427
         [kettle dings]         

54:26.763 --> 54:29.664
  No, I just had 'em in the...  
         back of my car,        

54:29.700 --> 54:31.767
and when I looked at the engine,
    I thought I'd put 'em on    

54:31.769 --> 54:33.035
       just so I don't get      
       oil on my clothes.       

54:34.571 --> 54:37.072
   Shame you weren't that OCD   
    when you were growing up,   

54:37.108 --> 54:40.275
     because I swear there's    
   still bacteria in that room  

54:40.343 --> 54:42.278
      a scientist couldn't      
         put a name to.         

54:48.919 --> 54:50.286
             You OK?            

54:51.555 --> 54:52.721
              Yeah.             

54:59.896 --> 55:01.463
            Rodger...           

55:06.437 --> 55:09.038
   did you know my dad before   
    you and Mum got married?    

55:10.808 --> 55:12.875
       Oh, no, not really.      

55:15.146 --> 55:16.445
       Well, not early on.      

55:17.447 --> 55:19.948
     You know, when I first     
      met your mum, I'd...      

55:19.983 --> 55:23.819
  just flown in to install the  
   phones at the post office.   

55:25.089 --> 55:27.322
 She came in a few times, but...

55:27.391 --> 55:29.491
  I don't remember your father  
         being with her.        

55:30.126 --> 55:31.727
    He may have been, though.   

55:33.063 --> 55:34.496
            Why, son?           

55:35.765 --> 55:38.133
        So, the fact that       
       you didn't know him      

55:38.168 --> 55:40.436
 probably made it easier for you

55:41.071 --> 55:42.638
     when he killed himself.    

55:45.809 --> 55:46.508
            [scoffs]            

55:47.344 --> 55:49.912
        Jesus, none of it       
         was easy, mate.        

55:51.081 --> 55:54.016
      You know, it was all      
      a terrible business.      

55:54.951 --> 55:56.518
       Terrible business?       

55:59.856 --> 56:00.922
              Yeah.             

56:00.957 --> 56:02.257
         [clears throat]        

56:02.292 --> 56:04.660
 How was it a terrible business?

56:07.331 --> 56:08.997
     Well, your father's...     

56:11.535 --> 56:12.868
       No-one expected it.      

56:14.204 --> 56:17.873
  Most of all, your mother, who 
 took it very hard, as you know.

56:19.042 --> 56:20.976
    And of course, you boys.    

56:22.446 --> 56:24.012
       What about us boys?      

56:25.982 --> 56:28.817
  Well, not you so much, 'cause 
   you were only seven, but...  

56:30.220 --> 56:32.521
  it affected Jeff very deeply. 

56:33.790 --> 56:37.059
 You know, he completely closed 
   down for a couple of weeks.  

56:39.129 --> 56:42.297
  Then when he finally did talk 
  to me, he made it very clear  

56:42.332 --> 56:47.169
  that, you know, you boys had  
 one father and one father only.

56:49.506 --> 56:50.706
         [Terry] He did?        

56:52.042 --> 56:54.476
 [Rodger] Yeah, well, of course.
       I understood that.       

56:55.913 --> 56:58.847
You know, it isn't easy stepping
   into another man's shoes.    

57:00.083 --> 57:03.585
   You know, especially under   
       such circumstances.      

57:05.755 --> 57:07.923
      [Terry] You probably      
         preferred to...        

57:08.759 --> 57:10.926
  spend time with your radios.  

57:13.430 --> 57:15.764
     That's a little harsh,     
     don't you think, Terry?    

57:16.667 --> 57:19.435
       What I meant was I       
         respected that.        

57:20.437 --> 57:22.570
       And I made it clear      
       to him that I would      

57:22.606 --> 57:25.107
      never take the place      
         of your father.        

57:30.548 --> 57:33.014
  You know, what happened back  
   then was hard on you both,   

57:33.049 --> 57:36.452
   it was hard on your mother,  
     and it was hard on me.     

57:40.123 --> 57:44.059
 Was it as hard as leaving your 
  own kids back in Queensland?  

57:49.199 --> 57:53.035
 OK, look, yeah, I can see that 
  you're upset about something, 

57:53.070 --> 57:54.602
      so... just tell me--      

57:54.638 --> 57:56.805
    - Do you want some milk?    
        - No, thank you.        

57:58.275 --> 57:59.241
      I don't want any tea.     

58:00.710 --> 58:03.479
  You know, I've had a long day 
   with your mother's doctors.  

58:04.748 --> 58:07.315
      And I've still got to     
     brush and shoe Freddie.    

58:07.317 --> 58:09.084
        Now, I don't know       
        what's going on,        

58:09.986 --> 58:11.653
           but before           
        either of us say        

58:11.722 --> 58:14.289
        something that we       
        can't take back,        

58:14.324 --> 58:16.558
        let's just settle       
        this conversation       

58:16.593 --> 58:18.660
          down a little         
         bit and try...         

58:19.997 --> 58:21.897
      Wait a Gypsy minute.      

58:23.733 --> 58:25.600
You're supposed to be in Sydney.

58:25.635 --> 58:27.669
  [Jeff] Hit the fuckin' deck!  

58:27.738 --> 58:29.604
     Hands in front of you!     
           Head down!           

58:29.639 --> 58:31.840
   Look the other fuckin' way!  
   Hands on your fuckin' head!  

58:31.842 --> 58:34.275
     This. Put them on him.     
         Bind his hands.        

58:34.311 --> 58:36.311
           - Quickly!           
        - [Rodger groans]       

58:36.346 --> 58:38.246
       Don't fuckin' move!      

58:38.281 --> 58:39.614
        OK. Bind them up.       

58:39.649 --> 58:41.850
       - [Rodger mutters]       
        - [Jeff] Shut up!       

58:41.852 --> 58:44.753
       Stop looking at me!      
       Here, put this on.       

58:44.788 --> 58:46.522
        Come around here.       
    Put it on back to front.    

58:46.524 --> 58:50.325
 Not you, the fucking balaclava!
        Come on, come on!       

58:50.360 --> 58:52.193
  Alright. Give me your hands.  

58:52.262 --> 58:54.029
      Both hands together!      

58:55.198 --> 58:56.965
           Hands down!          

58:57.000 --> 58:59.668
      What the fuck, Jeff?      
       Take the mask off!       

59:00.037 --> 59:01.036
           Get the...           

59:10.213 --> 59:11.647
             Jeff?!             

59:13.984 --> 59:16.818
          [door creaks]         

59:16.853 --> 59:18.153
               J?!              

59:22.159 --> 59:23.724
         [water sloshes]        

59:23.726 --> 59:25.493
[Jeff in distance] Get in there!

59:25.528 --> 59:26.962
              Jeff?             

59:29.199 --> 59:30.732
            Untie me!           

59:33.069 --> 59:34.670
              Jeff!             

59:38.742 --> 59:39.708
               J!               

59:39.743 --> 59:41.243
        [object clatters]       

59:42.979 --> 59:44.079
            [grunts]            

59:45.382 --> 59:46.848
         Tez. Easy, Tez.        

59:48.218 --> 59:49.684
         Where's Rodger?        

59:49.719 --> 59:52.053
  Look, I know you didn't want  
     to be involved in this     

59:52.088 --> 59:54.689
      and I know you wanted     
       me to do it alone.       

59:54.724 --> 59:57.059
   But, mate, he's got old man  
   strength. I need your help.  

59:57.928 --> 59:59.695
  We've got to do it together.  

01:00:02.065 --> 01:00:03.331
       [muffled grunting]       

01:00:03.366 --> 01:00:05.400
         [water sloshes]        

01:00:05.435 --> 01:00:08.103
      [thumping, grunting]      

01:00:13.543 --> 01:00:15.877
        [muffled yelping]       

01:00:25.388 --> 01:00:27.122
            [grunts]            

01:00:33.630 --> 01:00:35.763
            [grunts]            

01:00:35.798 --> 01:00:37.599
  Terry, get in here and help!  

01:00:37.634 --> 01:00:40.201
       Terry, get in here!      
        Get in here now!        

01:00:40.236 --> 01:00:42.037
     [Rodger tries to yell]     

01:00:48.745 --> 01:00:50.478
  Hold him down. Hold him down. 

01:00:50.480 --> 01:00:55.217
           - [grunts]           
  - Rodger, shh, shh. Shh, shh. 

01:00:58.055 --> 01:00:59.821
        Shit! Fuck, fuck!       

01:01:01.558 --> 01:01:03.591
         What the fuck?!        

01:01:03.627 --> 01:01:05.260
          [radio blares         
        Mozart's Requiem]       

01:01:05.295 --> 01:01:05.760
               No!              

01:01:05.796 --> 01:01:07.329
       No, no, don't! No!       

01:01:07.397 --> 01:01:08.930
         - [music stops]        
             - Jeff!            

01:01:11.635 --> 01:01:12.968
     [Rodger tries to yell]     

01:01:14.504 --> 01:01:16.738
   [Rodger grunts frantically]  

01:01:18.075 --> 01:01:19.274
         [radio blares]         

01:01:19.309 --> 01:01:21.243
      - Look out! Look out!     
       - [Rodger screams]       

01:01:22.746 --> 01:01:24.746
     [electricity crackles]     

01:01:24.782 --> 01:01:27.849
     [radio plays <i> Confutatis</i>    
     from Mozart's Requiem]     

01:01:42.366 --> 01:01:44.199
          [music stops]         

01:01:45.202 --> 01:01:47.369
        [Terry whimpers]        

01:01:50.340 --> 01:01:53.375
         [Terry screams]        

01:01:56.880 --> 01:01:58.046
    The fuse must have gone.    

01:01:59.049 --> 01:02:02.484
      What the fuck, Jeff?!     
    What the fuck was that?!    

01:02:03.220 --> 01:02:04.853
           It's over.           

01:02:05.555 --> 01:02:07.189
           We did it.           

01:02:38.655 --> 01:02:40.255
    Dad's watch has stopped.    

01:02:41.357 --> 01:02:43.825
    Made it through two years   
     at war. It'll be fine.     

01:02:44.361 --> 01:02:46.261
        It's waterproof.        

01:02:47.263 --> 01:02:48.763
             [sighs]            

01:02:48.765 --> 01:02:51.432
  OK, Tez. I think we're gonna  
     have to make a move...     

01:02:51.434 --> 01:02:52.833
         Don't touch me!        

01:02:52.869 --> 01:02:55.169
        My name is Terry.       
      Stop calling me Tez.      

01:02:55.204 --> 01:02:57.072
      Stop calling me that.     
       I fucking hate it!       

01:02:58.575 --> 01:03:01.176
  Would you... would you like a 
little moment alone with Rodger?

01:03:01.211 --> 01:03:02.277
               No.              

01:03:02.279 --> 01:03:04.780
          We leave now!         

01:03:06.416 --> 01:03:07.615
            Terry...            

01:03:07.617 --> 01:03:10.551
   Now, we can't go just yet.   

01:03:10.587 --> 01:03:13.789
      OK, you get dressed,      
        I'll prep Rodger.       

01:03:17.794 --> 01:03:19.127
              Fuck!             

01:03:58.835 --> 01:04:01.002
      [mechanical whirring]     

01:04:10.613 --> 01:04:12.981
    OK. We've got a problem.    

01:04:15.352 --> 01:04:18.520
       Rodger's phone. It       
        needs a password.       

01:04:20.357 --> 01:04:21.923
         Do you know it?        

01:04:23.493 --> 01:04:24.859
             [sighs]            

01:04:24.928 --> 01:04:26.794
           OK. Well...          

01:04:26.829 --> 01:04:28.129
         Doesn't matter.        

01:04:28.164 --> 01:04:30.598
        Like Dad, 40% of        
       people that commit       

01:04:30.633 --> 01:04:32.800
       suicide don't leave      
          a note, so...         

01:04:32.836 --> 01:04:34.536
    uh, we should be alright.   

01:04:46.215 --> 01:04:48.450
             [sighs]            

01:04:48.485 --> 01:04:51.953
        [phone vibrates]        

01:05:03.800 --> 01:05:06.234
         [ringing tone]         

01:05:15.745 --> 01:05:17.145
        Are you OK, mate?       

01:05:18.381 --> 01:05:20.081
             - Yeah.            
            - Terry.            

01:05:21.251 --> 01:05:22.417
           Are you OK?          

01:05:22.719 --> 01:05:24.252
              Yes.              

01:05:25.756 --> 01:05:27.656
       I'm sorry, brother.      

01:05:28.258 --> 01:05:30.091
           I'm sorry.           

01:05:32.896 --> 01:05:34.362
         I'm very sorry.        

01:05:36.766 --> 01:05:38.433
          [horn honks]          

01:05:38.901 --> 01:05:41.102
          [toots horn]          

01:05:45.275 --> 01:05:47.609
Fucking horse guy isn't due here
       for another hour.        

01:05:52.048 --> 01:05:53.515
          - I'll check.         
          - No, no, no.         

01:05:53.550 --> 01:05:55.550
   You stay here. I'll check.   

01:05:58.020 --> 01:05:59.787
     Jeff, don't touch that.    
          If the light          

01:05:59.856 --> 01:06:02.123
        goes out, they'll       
      know someone's here.      

01:06:07.063 --> 01:06:09.965
       - You see anything?      
              - No.             

01:06:31.054 --> 01:06:33.488
         [door rattles]         

01:06:47.436 --> 01:06:49.004
             [pants]            

01:06:56.146 --> 01:06:58.613
    - Who the fuck is that?!    
         - I don't know.        

01:06:59.082 --> 01:07:01.149
         Whoever it is,         

01:07:01.184 --> 01:07:03.351
   they knew where the fuckin'  
      spare key was hidden.     

01:07:07.657 --> 01:07:09.323
       You don't think...?      

01:07:09.358 --> 01:07:10.792
              What?             

01:07:10.827 --> 01:07:12.694
          [Mum] Rodger?         

01:07:14.197 --> 01:07:16.331
 It's bloody freezin' out there.

01:07:17.801 --> 01:07:19.199
         [sighs wearily]        

01:07:19.268 --> 01:07:22.303
  I'm gonna make a cuppa, love. 
          You want one?         

01:07:23.172 --> 01:07:25.306
    [walking frame clatters]    

01:07:29.813 --> 01:07:31.513
         [flicks switch]        

01:07:32.782 --> 01:07:34.215
     She cannot be in here!     

01:07:34.217 --> 01:07:36.050
   What are you talking about?  
         She's in, mate.        

01:07:36.052 --> 01:07:38.119
   We're fuckin' done. [pants]  

01:07:38.155 --> 01:07:40.455
 Then we have to get out of here
       before she sees us.      

01:07:41.825 --> 01:07:43.124
          - [sighs] Oh!         
             - What?            

01:07:43.159 --> 01:07:44.793
  Our bags are in the kitchen.  

01:07:51.067 --> 01:07:52.834
             [pants]            

01:07:55.071 --> 01:07:57.672
       [sighs] Oh, Rodger.      

01:07:59.142 --> 01:08:02.844
       Why don't you wear       
    your bloody hearing aid?    

01:08:05.848 --> 01:08:07.214
            Oh, fuck.           

01:08:07.249 --> 01:08:09.083
     OK, we need to distract    
         her and get our        

01:08:09.152 --> 01:08:10.852
        bags and get the        
        fuck out of here.       

